nodes.text: Imperial Shuttle 9604 was a Lambda-class T-4a shuttle used by Diplomatic Service branch of Imperial Intelligence of the Galactic Empire.

In 3 BBY this shuttle was used by Imperial agent Jahan Cross and his droid companion IN-GA 44 to travel to Etti IV to follow a lead on the Iron Eclipse project. They arrived at Mondder Spaceport on Imperial Pad 693 to meet with the Imperial Advisor to the Corporate Sector, Blains Vorlin.
